        <h2>
            中国未来核潜艇力量的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7426171">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7426171/" class="title-link">艇长完胜学院派</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7426171"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3486579/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3486579-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3486579/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">shumi2</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-27"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-27 12:28:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7426171_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书中的多数文章是由海军战争学院的教授们攥写，成文于十年前，放在今年看来，也无外乎剪刀+浆糊之作，没有超出这些年公开的中文出版物或网络文字的内容深度，不看也罢。 全书最有价值的是几位前核潜艇军官的观点，尤其是两篇从回顾冷战期间美苏核潜艇对抗战略战术来展望中国...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7426171/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
